query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('ansible',
'apache-spark',
'blob',
'erlang',
'global',
'java-8',
'odoo',
'pyqt4',
'sitecore',
'soapui',
'tidyverse',
'visualization');
